A Studio Ghibli-style illustration of a curious young child sitting cross-legged on a bedroom floor, surrounded by colorful floating puzzle pieces and geometric building blocks that swirl magically in the air around them. The child reaches up with wonder toward the hovering shapes, which glow softly with warm amber and teal light. A friendly robotic cat companion sits beside them, its eyes glowing with gentle curiosity. Through a large window, a dreamy twilight sky with soft pink and purple clouds. The room is cozy and cluttered with creative toys, gears, and whimsical mechanical creatures in various stages of assembly. Warm, painterly brushstrokes with characteristic Ghibli soft lighting and attention to atmospheric detail.
